// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// SD SELF-INCLUDE LOOP BODY (hierarchical version)
//
// Uses three-dimensional counter: T<T2><T1>_Y<Y2><Y1>_M<M1>
// T = trait ID (set at trait definition time)
// Y = type ID per trait (incremented once per impl, after all methods)
// M = method index (= ___TRAIT_SD_PASS, 0-7)
//
// The flat SD counter (C1-C7) is still incremented for _Generic iteration.
// Before the first method: restore Y counter for this trait
// After the last method: increment Y counter and save
